OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPlan to shut war crimes    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fprobe concerned minister   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Veterans Minister Johnny Mercer raised 
OL,6, serious concerns in government in 2019 
OL,7, over the decision to close an          
OL,8, investigation into UK special forces.  
OL,10,FThe BBC understands that Mr Mercer     
OL,11,Fwrote to then-defence secretary Ben    
OL,12,FWallace to warn against the closure.   
OL,14,FThe veterans minister, a former British
OL,15,Farmy officer, was privately concerned  
OL,16,Fthat there were credible war crimes    
OL,17,Fallegations against British forces.    
OL,19,FWhen the closure was later announced,  
OL,20,FMr Mercer publicly backed the decision.
